00:00:00,125 --> 00:00:01,918
Kam rungan’ morunga’agen
fare Babyor ku Mormon,

2
00:00:01,918 --> 00:00:04,542
machane gamed ra balyangaen'med
napan ni ngam fil’ed morunga’agen.

3
00:00:04,542 --> 00:00:05,083
Utangaen,

4
00:00:05,083 --> 00:00:09,042
binir e cheppen morunga'agen e
nam nib ga’ ufithik’ biyu’ e duw.

5
00:00:09,042 --> 00:00:09,959
U gum’ircha’en,

6
00:00:09,959 --> 00:00:14,542
binir ma weliy morunga’agen e gidii
ni ma guy rogon me fol Yesus Kristus.

7
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:17,876
Me tabab u Jerusalem chuchugur
ko 600 BC napan e profet

8
00:00:17,876 --> 00:00:21,334
i chiyliy Got ngak’ morunga’agen
e gathay nag ko binaw.

9
00:00:21,334 --> 00:00:26,000
Cha’nem nge tabinaw rok’ kar th’aebed
farengi day nga Mariken nib kakrom.

10
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,876
Kar ga’nag e gidii’ nge
kii’egrad u but’ ko la’agruw

11
00:00:28,876 --> 00:00:31,709
e nam nib ga’ nibay e
ngiyal’ ko mael nge gapas.

12
00:00:31,709 --> 00:00:36,250
Pi yafos rorad nira pii’ athamgil ngomed
ni ngam thapeg e mich u Yesus Kristus,

13
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:38,250
fol ko pi motochiyl, nge pigpig.

14
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:41,167
Bay e pi thin nib thothup rorad
e pi profet ulan fare Babyor

15
00:00:41,167 --> 00:00:43,876
ku Mormon nima micheg
morunga’agen e yib ko Tathapeg.

16
00:00:43,876 --> 00:00:46,334
Me gelnag e tin nib riyul’
ko fare Bible nge pii’

17
00:00:46,334 --> 00:00:48,667
e m’ag ni Yesus Kristus
ir Facha’ ni Fak Got;

18
00:00:48,667 --> 00:00:53,167
ni Ke fas, yim’,
nge gelnag e yim’ nge denen nifan gubindad.

19
00:00:53,167 --> 00:00:57,083
Arfan ni bay noeg “Reb e
M’ag rok’ Yesus Kristus.”

20
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:57,667
Ba riyul’,

21
00:00:57,667 --> 00:01:01,542
pin’en nib ga’ ulan e babyor ney
ir fare ngiyal’ Yesus Kristus

22
00:01:01,542 --> 00:01:05,667
nike yib nga gidii’ ulan e Mariken
tomur e faskoyam’ u Jerusalem.

23
00:01:05,667 --> 00:01:08,626
Ke machib e gospel Rok’,
I gol nagraed ko m’ar,

24
00:01:08,626 --> 00:01:10,125
nge yibilynag pi bitir.

25
00:01:10,125 --> 00:01:12,918
Machane binem ir kemus e tabab ko yaat ney.

26
00:01:12,918 --> 00:01:16,042
Gelngen nib ga’ ko fare
Babyor ku Mormon ni'ir e

27
00:01:16,042 --> 00:01:19,375
rogon ni ma ayuwegmed nifan
e magawon romed daba’.

28
00:01:19,375 --> 00:01:21,250
Rangam pir’eg e gapas, fanow,

29
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:25,417
nge fil urogon ni ngam mang e
bee’ nib fel’ nge nib falfalaen’.

30
00:01:25,417 --> 00:01:25,918
Nib ga’,

31
00:01:25,918 --> 00:01:30,083
rayog ni ngam chuchugur ngak e
Tathapeg rom ni Yesus Kristus.

